            <p>Our purpose is to show those with dyslexia, that their ‘abilities’… don’t have to disable their happiness, or hinder their right to feel one with everyone else. Its difficult sometimes to accept you are different from everyone else because everyone wants to belong somewhere or be apart of something. We are that place. We are those people. With us everyone belongs. As well as gets an equal chance at recognition because that’s what you, the people, deserve.</p>
